            "achievements": "30+ years of clinical practice\nFellowship-trained in Anti-Aging Medicine (FAARM)\nPublished researcher in hormone optimization\nMedical faculty at multiple institutions\nMedical Advisory Board Member, Igniton™",
            "education": "<p><strong>Medical Degree:</strong> Doctor of Medicine (M.D.)</p><p><strong>Board Certification:</strong> Obstetrics & Gynecology (FACOG)</p><p><strong>Fellowship:</strong> Anti-Aging, Regenerative & Functional Medicine</p>",
            "publications_research": "<p>Dr. King has authored peer-reviewed research on hormone optimization, longevity interventions, and integrative approaches to age-related conditions. Her work bridges conventional medicine with cutting-edge functional and regenerative therapies.</p>",
            "board_certifications": "American Board of Obstetrics & Gynecology (FACOG)\nFellow, American Academy of Anti-Aging Medicine (FAARM)\nIntegrative Medicine Certification",
            "card_accent_color": "#191880"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "team_member",
          "settings": {
            "full_name": "Dr. Konstantin Korotkov",
            "credentials": "PhD",
            "title": "Professor of Physics & Bioelectrography Pioneer",
            "name_initial": "K",
            "short_bio": "Internationally acclaimed scientist and inventor of Gas Discharge Visualization (GDV) technology, revolutionizing the study of human energy fields.",
            "bio_page": "",
            "specialties": "Bioelectrography\nQuantum Biology\nEnergy Medicine\nHuman Energy Fields\nBiophysics",
            "achievements": "200+ published scientific papers\n15+ international patents\nProfessor of Physics, St. Petersburg University\nConsultant to NASA and Russian Olympic Committee\nPioneer of GDV/EPI technology\nMedical Advisory Board Member, Igniton™",
